description: After a quick and easy dinner idea? This warming prawn and chicken laksa will be on the table in just 20 minutes.
name: Chicken & Prawn Laksa Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Meanwhile, cook noodles according to packet instructions. Drain. Divide noodles among bowls. Ladle over broth mixture. Top with sprouts, mint and chilli. Serve with lime wedges.
